{"tid":544622,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"HR/勞工法 試用期問題","createTime":"2018-01-29T16:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T17:40:29.000Z","uid":55379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5274fb1ed1df81efc21d4fd51111592aee553738","tid":544622,"uid":55379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f1a40cde203fc1cd022f856a9088ea8aa4ff19","tid":544622,"uid":52406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T17:12:47.000Z","msg":"未夠三個月唔使畀年假你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65a914928040c1484a047c2352702edcb32e435","tid":544622,"uid":55379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T17:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未夠三個月唔使畀年假你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣係勞工法例定左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？咁如果過三個月又唔過六個月呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1097dc05e076e69820685d3cdadc279fd47351","tid":544622,"uid":77251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:35:52.000Z","msg":"問5.\t僱員受僱未滿一年辭職，僱主是否須按比例給予僱員年假薪酬？ <br />\n答5.\t<br />\n如僱員在一個假期年內受僱滿3個月但不足12個月，除因犯嚴重過失而遭即時解僱外，則不論以任何理由終止僱傭合約，都可獲發放按比例計算的年假薪酬。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57i_whole.htm#Q5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ffaq%2Fcap57i_whole.htm%23Q5&d=btCVXQQjrXwPBq5llfxgH4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=8eec6b2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/faq/cap57i_whole.htm#Q5</a>"},{"pid":"f8b6f1ae5c05002003faaae9a2af14f5a1e7cb4a","tid":544622,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"你未過試用 應該唔會比"},{"pid":"d0b112ab94cee420c8291d3b6442540a41f801be","tid":544622,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T03:02:14.000Z","msg":"試用期淨係同通知期掛勾<br />\n大假勞工假都係做夠3個月起錶"},{"pid":"b46bfcb2871ec7fbeb88cbb3528ea512bdd55b62","tid":544622,"uid":55379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試用期淨係同通知期掛勾<br />\n大假勞工假都係做夠3個月起錶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁正常公司都唔會勞工假唔計糧俾你，之但係佢有冇權扣返頭三個月勞工假嘅人工呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554ea81a7fc78d48a376874613efc1889f4def05","tid":544622,"uid":11462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fa6b8faf0cf4e73280e90a2798f20cd6648e1a","tid":544622,"uid":11462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"554ea81a7fc78d48a376874613efc1889f4def05","tid":544622,"uid":11462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ad823eebee43b520ad963ab9c34025fce42b0c","tid":544622,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85fa6b8faf0cf4e73280e90a2798f20cd6648e1a","tid":544622,"uid":11462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"554ea81a7fc78d48a376874613efc1889f4def05","tid":544622,"uid":11462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T17:05:05.000Z","msg":"唔關probation事，而係關做滿三個月事"},{"pid":"22932ea5d2bbc2fc5203d6a1136b82c753e82197","tid":544622,"uid":27349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:10:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cb19e9e4e7c993b6776f0c562c843ed1844b1c2","tid":544622,"uid":167294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:40:29.000Z","msg":"如果出糧係底薪加佣 <br />\n我做左個幾月即走 賠比公司嘅7日代通知金係計全部除31x7定底薪除31x7 ?<br />\n<br />\n同埋未過三個月勞工假係咪當np pay嫁？"}]}